Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.80,0:01:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.12,0:01:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真差勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.52,0:01:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,涉那小子一點都沒進步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.33,0:02:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.11,0:02:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.54,0:02:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓開路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.94,0:02:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點 要過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.42,0:02:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看著 最強的車手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.81,0:02:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厲害 太帥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.05,0:02:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰都不能模仿吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒問題 過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.65,0:02:42.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彎道出口會遇到對向車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.02,0:02:43.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓出內線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.03,0:02:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下個彎沒有對向車 留五厘米 很多沙子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛剛好 開得不錯 狀態非常好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的話遇到誰都不會輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.12,0:03:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\pos(135,256)\fs20\fad(650,750)}碓冰山道的天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.53,0:03:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.91,0:03:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次見面的女孩會突然給你電話號碼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰相信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.94,0:03:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肯定是哪裏弄錯了 弄錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.34,0:03:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊 池谷前輩 沒那麼簡單的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就以我來說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.23,0:03:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像我這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.46,0:03:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車手不需要女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.85,0:03:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關鍵是沒弄錯的話就不像池谷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.96,0:03:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不像我是什麼意思啊? 健二
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就那麼蠢嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可照你說的也太順利了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.32,0:04:04.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭啊 你們那種妒忌別人幸福的表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.90,0:04:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那隨風飄動的棕色長髮...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.42,0:04:12.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回頭看我時 那雙水汪汪的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.43,0:04:18.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想她一定是神為了獎勵認真工作的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而派來人間的天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.74,0:04:25.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明天星期日 去輕井澤見真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.90,0:04:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工作 工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.23,0:04:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說 我們也悄悄跟在後面看看那女孩到底什麼樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去啊 去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.03,0:04:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去親眼看清楚到底是什麼樣的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 被池谷前輩發現了怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.33,0:04:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別擔心 以現在池谷的狀態不可能發現吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.83,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好好看清楚傳說中的真子到底長什麼樣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別妨礙池谷哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.97,0:05:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會妨礙他的 前輩被甩時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會和他一起哭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.07,0:05:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是火熱的友情啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.14,0:05:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說他被甩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.72,0:05:33.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正真人肯定沒他說的那麼可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.69,0:05:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙喜歡大驚小怪 自以為是得很
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.92,0:05:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得是在中學時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.47,0:05:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一次和他去秋名湖釣魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.73,0:05:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們倆一條魚都沒釣到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.35,0:05:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快要回去時 我終於釣到一條小魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.02,0:05:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後池谷那傢伙就興奮地大喊「哇 好大」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.52,0:05:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實才這麼大...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知情的大叔們還特地跑來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.01,0:06:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那時真是羞死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.07,0:06:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷真是個大驚小怪的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健二前輩 旁邊旁邊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.99,0:06:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕 說得入神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下意識地右腳用力...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.91,0:06:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本打算跟蹤 結果卻追上他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 池谷 原諒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只想來看看真子長什麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的只是為了這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全沒想過要妨礙你約會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.72,0:06:37.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別生氣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.62,0:06:40.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會在下個出入口掉頭的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.11,0:06:45.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真沒辦法 不回去也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.39,0:06:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也不介意介紹給你們認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.44,0:06:50.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.57,0:06:53.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...之後就別再跟來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.91,0:06:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真的會生氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.17,0:06:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.82,0:06:58.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次見面 我叫佐藤真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.89,0:07:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.45,0:07:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.36,0:07:31.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在做夢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.82,0:07:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來不像做夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我受了好大的打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.76,0:07:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼池谷會和那麼可愛的女孩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.68,0:07:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車手不需要女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.08,0:07:54.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,健二前輩 一起哭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.57,0:07:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說我找不到女朋友?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.31,0:08:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 開玩笑的 玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.68,0:08:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那接下來我們怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.09,0:08:13.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這時候的輕井澤可不合適三個大男人溜達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如去碓冰山道看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.44,0:08:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子你喜愛什麼樣的車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.92,0:08:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,談不上喜愛...以前嚮往過前一代的RX7
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.62,0:08:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,FC啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.75,0:08:53.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很雅致的愛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生是車手吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.06,0:09:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然知道啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.16,0:09:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過今天打算和普通駕駛員一樣兜兜風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.68,0:09:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問...真子...這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.74,0:09:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對男人當車手有什麼看法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.84,0:09:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯啊 因為我也喜歡車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.98,0:09:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.15,0:09:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,車手果然比普通人開得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.45,0:09:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好車子有錢就能買到 但技術是買不回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.55,0:09:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得應變技術好的人比開昂貴外國車的人更帥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.17,0:09:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好女孩 理想的女孩啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這就是碓冰山道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.53,0:10:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是第一次開 比想像中更困難的迂迴道路啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.52,0:10:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣全都是彎道 路面又狹窄...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.46,0:10:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和秋名比起來似是而非啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.82,0:10:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在碓冰最快的不知道是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.10,0:10:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問...池谷先生...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.43,0:10:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.19,0:10:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從男人的角度看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.21,0:10:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你對喜歡山道 做出像車手般舉動的女孩...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.49,0:10:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼看法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sil-80?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.05,0:10:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的 聽聞藍色的Sil-80是現在最快的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.86,0:10:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外別吃驚哦 那車手是女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.74,0:10:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.80,0:10:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女車手嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.51,0:10:55.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯啊 完全沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.89,0:11:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再好不過 感覺女車手反而能有共同語言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.31,0:11:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.83,0:11:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此 明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.41,0:11:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子想成為車手 所以嚮往的車會是FC
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.72,0:11:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女孩開的Sil-80啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.15,0:11:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問 Sil-80是...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,外國車嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.41,0:11:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.81,0:11:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sil-80就是180配上Silvia前臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.47,0:11:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是Silvia和180的結合版所以叫Sil-80
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.06,0:11:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個車手是碓冰山道最快的車手 而且還是個女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真想見識見識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等到晚上的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該能在碓冰山道見到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.89,0:11:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過還是千萬別和她比賽的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.58,0:11:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為本地都沒人能贏她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.21,0:12:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秋名SPEED STARS就是我組建的車隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.32,0:12:12.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在被稱為秋名最快的車手就在我們隊裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的後輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.56,0:12:17.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,論速度的話 接下來就是我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.78,0:12:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了? 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.75,0:12:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.29,0:12:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 好像都在說車的事 很無聊吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.72,0:12:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 沒這回事 我也非常喜歡車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.87,0:12:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.76,0:12:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎...那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.74,0:12:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.89,0:12:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真子難道也是因為漂移的魅力才嚮往成為車手的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.41,0:12:45.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.52,0:12:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒我這點水平的話很難掌握的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.59,0:12:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為這是很危險的技術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.45,0:12:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生你也很擅長漂移?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.43,0:12:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.56,0:12:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.42,0:13:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.29,0:13:11.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝你 今天很開心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.65,0:13:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問 真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.93,0:13:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.75,0:13:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請問 真子...這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.79,0:13:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你現在交往的人...這個...有嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.29,0:13:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒有男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.16,0:13:35.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以...請再打電話給我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.00,0:13:36.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.86,0:13:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷 聽得見嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.05,0:13:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前輩 醒醒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.81,0:13:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們還在啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.55,0:14:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裏 太擔心前輩了所以想回去也沒回成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.58,0:14:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣? 順利嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.59,0:14:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天真是個好日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.89,0:14:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就去吃飯吧 我好久沒請客了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.91,0:14:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順便去瞧瞧碓冰的車手是怎麼跑的 也不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.87,0:14:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來似乎進展順利呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.71,0:14:26.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇跡這東西還真有的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不錯啊 碓冰所有車手水平都很高啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.00,0:14:38.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.60,0:14:42.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是第一次來秋名以外的山道吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.45,0:14:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.69,0:14:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.41,0:14:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒親手握著方向盤 所以不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.83,0:14:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎? 可看你用特別認真的眼神盯著彎道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.14,0:14:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和現在的眼神完全不一樣哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,根本不像同一個人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.28,0:15:02.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣? 能跑嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.13,0:15:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事不跑怎麼知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.87,0:15:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.88,0:15:08.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Sil-80嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.45,0:15:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連續逆漂移!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.96,0:15:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好厲害 很高明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.79,0:15:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才的看到了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.02,0:15:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,狹窄的道路上仍然迫力十足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.57,0:15:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然很得意地和真子說自己擅長漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.85,0:15:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實連甩尾都害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.18,0:15:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去可不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.87,0:15:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再不認真努力的話 難得的天使就會離我而去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.84,0:15:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣下山回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.32,0:15:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.95,0:15:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管哪裏的路上都有厲害的傢伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.11,0:16:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷那傢伙特別拚命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.50,0:16:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裏可是乘了三人 追不上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.07,0:16:12.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離遠點比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.44,0:16:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺節奏有點問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.30,0:16:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前輩的車開得很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.60,0:16:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事你也看得出來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是很肯定 可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.59,0:16:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然失控了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.39,0:16:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和拓海說的一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.88,0:16:40.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好 有對向車要來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真危險 真是的 哪來的笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.44,0:16:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,害怕車尾太靠外就鬆了油門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像不忘找零的鄉巴佬一樣土得掉渣的初學者側滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜託 13的小哥 不快點讓開的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別的車陸續上來會很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.33,0:17:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就讓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷前輩也太丟臉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.58,0:17:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,醜死了 裝作不認識吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.52,0:17:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的很抱歉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.61,0:17:37.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.63,0:17:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.85,0:17:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,碓冰山道最快的Sil-80的車手竟然是真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.56,0:17:58.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想死的心都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.38,0:18:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請假?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,電話也不接
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.72,0:18:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個超認真工作的池谷?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.27,0:18:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天的事對他打擊很大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.51,0:18:16.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那以後都沒說過話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.12,0:18:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,服務區上廁所時也處於呆滯狀態 眼神空洞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.78,0:18:25.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很凄慘地一句話都不和我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.61,0:18:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早有不祥預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.24,0:18:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那女孩做池谷的女朋友實在可愛得過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.62,0:18:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正車手不需要女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.72,0:18:38.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤獨車手樹 這就是我的座右銘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.65,0:18:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望能早點走出陰影啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浩一郎 電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.98,0:18:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想接 就說我睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.39,0:18:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正多半是健二吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.77,0:19:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是女孩哦 叫佐藤真子的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.30,0:19:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說有話和我說...說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想戲弄我的話 就適可而止吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.21,0:19:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 戲弄什麼的怎麼可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.40,0:19:27.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,竟然駕駛著那麼厲害的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.42,0:19:34.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我看到了 那輛Sil-80厲害的漂移
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.56,0:19:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被稱為碓冰最快吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.98,0:19:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那麼厲害 至少也透露一點吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.49,0:19:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.39,0:19:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒打算隱瞞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.74,0:19:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天的事我也受了打擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.07,0:19:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我覺得必須說出實情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.17,0:19:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實情?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其實我性格很保守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保守? 難以置信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.25,0:20:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能做出那麼華麗漂移的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.07,0:20:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個...有些人一握方向盤人格就會改變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.63,0:20:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.21,0:20:16.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即使跑得再快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.38,0:20:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,男人也不會把我看作戀愛對像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.81,0:20:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,差不多也該結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.22,0:20:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經決定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.27,0:20:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今年夏天結束後就不做車手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為車手日子裏最後夏天的回憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.26,0:20:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請讓我和秋名的86在碓冰山道比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.62,0:20:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是我的願望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.72,0:20:43.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能成全我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.63,0:20:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.26,0:20:49.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把處女獻給池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.82,0:20:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 別說出那種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.82,0:20:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不想和我嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.28,0:20:58.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這個意思 那傢伙是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.10,0:21:01.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做不出這種像交易一般的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.94,0:21:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,徹底明白了 真子真正的目的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.97,0:21:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,並不是我 而是拓海
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.98,0:21:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.35,0:21:16.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不然這麼可愛的女孩怎麼會對我感興趣呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.77,0:21:25.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明白了 我盡力而為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.56,0:21:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但別誤會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.17,0:21:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我並不是為了報答而幫你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.71,0:21:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,池谷先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.20,0:21:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想完成你的心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.88,0:21:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.53,0:21:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然時間很短
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.51,0:21:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我真的很喜歡真子
